msgid "Standard Rate and Non-refundable Rate are two common rate plans. However, depending on your business, you can choose to set up the types of price differently, for example Breakfast Only, Half-Board, Full-Board etc.. would be a valid configuration as well. <br/>This wizard will suggest to create some default rate plans. If they do not match your needs, feel free to close this window to create your type(s) of price manually, even just one."
